          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1682613737487-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1682613737487-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Finely slice your <strong>white cup mushrooms</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat (if the pan is looking a little dry add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>)</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 5 min or until browned</p><p>Once the mushrooms have browned remove them from the heat and set aside (reserve the pan)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1682613741461-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1682613741461-x400.jpg",
