          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1682613749295-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half and put in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until starting to crisp</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once the béchamel sauce has thickened, add<strong> half </strong>the <strong>grated cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with a good grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>cheese sauce</strong></p><p>Set the<strong> cheese sauce</strong> aside to cool slightly</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1682613753987-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
